graph TD
    subgraph Client Application
        Web[React / Next.js Control Panel]
        Mobile[React Native Customer App]
    end

    subgraph AWS Cloud Infrastructure
        Gateway[API Gateway / Load Balancer]
        FastAPI[AWS EC2 / Dockerised FastAPI Backend]
        DB[(PostgreSQL / SQLite Database)]
        Cache[(Redis Cache Telemetry)]
    end

    subgraph Local Simulation
        SITL[PX4 Autopilot SITL]
        Gazebo[Gazebo classic simulation engine]
        AirSim[AirSim / UE5 simulation viewport]
    end

    Web <-->|WebSockets / REST| Gateway
    Mobile <-->|REST APIs| Gateway
    Gateway <--> FastAPI
    FastAPI <--> DB
    FastAPI <--> Cache
    
    SITL <-->|MAVLink / TCP| FastAPI
    SITL <-->|Physics API| Gazebo
    SITL <-->|Physics API| AirSim
